      "content": "i checked the ETA and it's not coming for at least 4 weeks. we have maybe 15 pairs left in the warehouse and we usually move 50+ a day. if we go 'out of stock' our ranking on the site is gonna tank and we'll lose all that momentum. is there any way we can just keep them listed as available for now? maybe we can just fulfill what we can and then deal with the delays later?",
